items.bio: I am a high functioning airhead.
Product owner. Techie. Golden Bear. Blue Devil. #KTBSPA. Bootcamp boxer. Hair Donor. Producer. Disney geek. Tree hugger. Listener. Animal lover. Wanderlust.

Hi! I am Carlin. Carlin I am.
I come from the dunes,
Where there is no ham.
Code by night, design by day;
Sleep is for the weak they say.
Hi! I'm Sean. This is where I share my search for my next big @SnackFixation (Instagram & Twitter).
50% chance my check-in is at oyster bar, ramen shop, sushi bar, or gym.
civic tech for engagement: usability, design, data, visualization, urban planning; working for the http://opentechinstitute.org  (@OTI)
